---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Journey" description="From a degraded 100-acre farm to a regenerating ecosystem — the founding, the design, and the outreach along the way." image="/images/pages/journey/hero.jpg" imageWidth={1280} imageHeight={960}>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Our Journey"
    title="From degraded farmland to a regenerating ecosystem"
    image="/images/pages/journey/hero.jpg"
    imageAlt="Early view of the farm during its restoration"
  />

  <section class="section wrapper">
    <h2>Early days</h2>
    <p>TVC is a 100-acre farm collectively owned by 53 families. Due to exploitative farming practices, the farmland was degraded when the collective bought it. Since 2017, the community has been using permaculture principles to regenerate the farm's fertility naturally.</p>

    <blockquote>
      <p>Nature does not hurry, yet everything is accomplished.</p>
      <cite>— Lao Tzu</cite>
    </blockquote>
  </section>

  <section class="section wrapper">
    <div class="explore-grid">
      <a class="card explore-card" href="/our-journey/timeline">
        <h3>Timeline</h3>
        <p>Nine years, year by year — tap through the story from a barren plot in 2017 to our first completed home, with photos for every month.</p>
        <span class="explore-link">Explore the timeline →</span>
      </a>
      <a class="card explore-card" href="/our-journey/design">
        <h3>The design</h3>
        <p>The permaculture principles behind the farm's layout — the wildlife corridor, food forests, and water works — plus a drone flyover.</p>
        <span class="explore-link">See the design →</span>
      </a>
      <a class="card explore-card" href="/our-journey/community-outreach">
        <h3>Community engagement &amp; outreach</h3>
        <p>Our work with the local community around the farm, in Odhipuram and Thaggatti village.</p>
        <span class="explore-link">See our outreach →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  blockquote {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--tvc-orange);
    padding: 4px 24px;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  blockquote cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 6px;
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--tvc-ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .explore-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .explore-card {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: box-shadow 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
  }

  .explore-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(34, 41, 31, 0.14);
  }

  .explore-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }

  .explore-card p {
    color: var(--tvc-ink-soft);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .explore-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 14px;
    color: var(--tvc-green);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
</style>
